attachments.title: The House From The Windows 95 Maze Screensaver Is Up For Sale
attachments.text: Get out your checkbooks, ’90s kids, because the iconic house that the Windows 95 maze screensaver was based on is now officially on the market. This northwest Washington chateau has been owned by Ron Fletcher for 30 years, but he’s looking to downsize from this winding, windowless labyrinth—which...

attachments.title: Video: The GoPro That Fell to Earth
attachments.text: In June 2013, members of the Grand Canyon Stratospheric Balloon Team launched a balloon with a camera into the stratosphere, where it burst. It was found by a hiker two years later.
